<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>249</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gimtheihna leh buoina khel khu,
 Aw ka thagau, thil zingin;
 Pathien thutiem kilang intin,
 Lungsietna ni lopi chuh.

[V2]
 Van Jubili, Van Jubili,
 Na ni lopi hung suok hen! (4)

[V3]
 2. India mite, Negro mite,
 Leh nam ngawng dang ten heu hen;
 Kalvari a hung kilang kha,
 Pathien zawhna lopi chuh.

[V4]
 Chanchin Pha chun, Chanchin Pha chun,
 Sim tawp, Mal tawp, hun thawng hen. (4)

[V5]
 3. Thim nuoi a um gam lien haw ah,
 Hukdamna vak tun sakin;
 Suohlam apat tumlam chan in,
 Khawvak chun zan nawh mang hen.

[V6]
 A tatna chuh, a tatna chuh,
 Chang u henla, khuovak hen. (4)

[V7]
 4. Sunni lopi chuh hung nai hen,
 Khawvak lopi hung lang hen;
 Kumkhuo tuonga Chanchin Pha chun,
 Na min gamtin ah phuong hen.

[V8]
 Gamtin cheng ah, Gamtin cheng ah,
 Immanuel gamtin ah. (4)

[V9]
 5. Gospel lengin, gamtin cheng ah,
 Guolzo zelin, hailo in;
 Na kumkhuo Lalgam lien tak chuh,
 Hung lien hen khangto zel hen.

[V10]
 Khawvel cheng cheng, Khawvel cheng cheng,
 Hukdampa, Na gam hi hen. (4)

[V11]
 6. Thilsiem tincheng - Gan leh lohing,
 Pathien guot banga um in;
 Pa, Chapa, Thagau Thieng pakin,
 Hehpih Pathien chawian leu.

[V12]
 Hallelujah! Hallelujah!
 Lei chung hi pakna'n dim hen. (4)</lyrics>
<title>OVER THE GLOOMY HILLS</title>
</song>